data.description: This is the house that you have been searching for, I guarantee it! A beautifully upgraded 4bedroom 2 full baths twin home. When you approach this fabulous home, a gorgeous modernized front porch greets you. Open the door where the foyer meets you with luxury vinyl planks, and the dining room boasts an impressive false designer ceiling. The house has custom window treatments on the main floor, and an expansive kitchen with upgraded flooring as well, to cook your heart out in! But that's not all. Second level has three generous sized rooms. The main bedroom features a designer closet for your heart's contentment, and all your shoes and accessories. Third floor has a full upgraded attic bedroom, with an oversized walk-in closet unlike any other you have seen. Go to the Basement and continue to entertain your family and guests with even more space. The outside deck is a wondrous place for you to relax and enjoy your morning coffee, while the kids play in the backyard with the privacy of their new vinyl fence. This house has GAS appliances, TWO parking spaces in the back, Central Air, and comes with a Clear CO from the City of Easton. Don't Blink on this one! Make your offer today! Please submit your offer by Monday 4/8 at 7pm, seller will make a decision on Tuesday morning.
